jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/ThyArtIsMurder-Chris-McMahon-leaves-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/ThyArtIsMurder-Chris-McMahon-leaves-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/ThyArtIsMurder-Chris-McMahon-leaves-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/ThyArtIsMurder-Chris-McMahon-leaves-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/en_au/artists/thy-art-is-murder">Thy Art Is Murder</a>分享了他们的新歌手与前主唱 Chris &#39;CJ&#39; McMahon 分手后的第一条信息。</p><p>去年九月，乐队在专辑《Godlike》发行一周后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/thy-art-is-murder-replace-frontman-on-new-album-due-to-a-breakdown-in-his-character-and-judgement-3503716">宣布与麦克马洪断绝关系</a>。 《你的艺术就是谋杀》在一份声明中称“他的性格和判断力崩溃了”。这支澳大利亚死亡核心乐队还表示，他们已经重新录制了这张专辑，以取代麦克马洪的声音。</p><p>麦克马洪最近因<a href="https://loudwire.com/cj-mcmahon-comments-dismissal-from-thy-art-is-murder/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">发表反跨性别言论而</a>受到批评，并在该组织的频道上道歉。乐队还声称麦克马洪威胁“如果我们不屈服于[麦克马洪]持有的各种意识形态，就会从内部摧毁你的艺术就是谋杀”。</p><p>在 10 月 4 日发布到社交媒体的视频中，乐队介绍了泰勒·米勒 (Tyler Miller) 作为他们的新主唱。米勒也是 Aversions Crown 的主唱。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/Cx_FiOYtofG/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></d